Package com.deprez

This package creates a simple database which is used in conjunction with simple plain old java objects for a simple swing application.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    The App class is a simple plain java object that manages appIds and appNames
    Community
    The Community class manages the list of User plain java objects.
    Database
    The database class that is used for read/write within the App Store project.
    Driver
    The main class of the project.
    Store
    The Store class manages the list of App plain java objects.
    User
    The plain java object of 'User' Contains User.userId and User.userName.
    UserAppReview
    Manages userId and appId pairs for better optimization compared to storing the each pair within Community and Store
    UserAppReviews
    The UserAppReviews class manages the list of UserAppReview plain java objects.

Package com.deprez Description

This package creates a simple database which is used in conjunction with simple plain old java objects for a simple swing application. This project is mainly for school, but I also plan to improve on it once I have learned more skills.

I plan to condense the project eventually. Diagrams ***WILL BE*** included alongside this package description.

Version:
1.0 5/17/2019
Author:
William Deprez
See Also:
java.awt, javax.swing, java.sql, java.util
